== Code ==
<pre>{{Infobox Berry
|name    =
|image   =
|caption =
|growtime  =
|harvest =
|replant =
|mutation =
|points =
|flavor =
|helditem =
}}</pre>

== Usage ==
To use this template, place the code above at the top of an article and fill in the respective blanks.

'''Where:'''
*<code>name</code> should be filled with the number of the berry in the dex (formatted #00) and the name of the berry.
*<code>image</code> should be filled with the berry's image.
*<code>caption</code> should be filled with the description of the berry from the in-game berrydex (or github).
*<code>growtime</code> should be filled with the time it takes for the berry to *fully* grow (with h/m/s as needed).
*<code>harvest</code> should be filled with the number of berries collected when manually harvesting the plant.
*<code>replant</code> should be filled with the replant rate of the berry.
*<code>mutation</code> should be filled with the mutation rate of the berry.
*<code>points</code> should be filled with the number of Farm Points gained on harvest ({{farmpoints}} is automatically added, don't add it yourself).
*<code>flavor</code> should be filled with the flavors of the berry. Copy and paste this code after the equals sign and fill in the numbers:
<pre><div style="clear:both;"></div>
* # spicy
* # dry
* # sweet
* # bitter
* # sour
</pre>
*<code>helditem</code> should only be included if the berry is dropped by a wild Pokémon. It should be filled with the names of each Pokémon that can drop the berry.
